a re-sign with Andretti Autosport|website=www.motorsport.com|language=en|access-date=2019-07-28}}</ref>\n|All\n|-\n|28\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Ryan Hunter-Reay]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.motorsport.com/indycar/news/andretti-autosport-re-signs-ryan-hunter-reay-dhl-828142/828142/|title=Andretti Autosport re-signs Ryan Hunter-Reay, DHL|website=www.motorsport.com|language=en|access-date=2019-05-28}}</ref>\n|All\n|-\n|29\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[James Hinchcliffe]]<ref name=\"Hinchcliffe AA\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.andrettiautosport.com/news/james-hinchcliffe-returns-to-andretti-autosport-for-three-indycar-races|title=Andretti Autosport {{!}} JAMES HINCHCLIFFE RETURNS TO ANDRETTI AUTOSPORT FOR THREE INDYCAR RACES|website=Andretti Autosport|language=en|access-date=2020-02-19}}</ref>\n|1, 4, 9\n|-\n|[[Andretti Autosport|Andretti]] [[Harding Steinbrenner Racing|Harding Steinbrenner Autosport]] \n|88\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Colton Herta]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://racer.com/2019/09/20/herta-to-join-andretti-in-fifth-steinbrenner-backed-entry-in-2020/|title=Herta to join Andretti in fifth Steinbrenner-backed entry in 2020|website=Racer.com|language=en|date=September 20, 2019|accessdate=September 20, 2019}}</ref>\n|All\n|-\n|[[Andretti Autosport|Andretti]] [[Bryan Herta Autosport|Herta Autosport]] w/ [[Marco Andretti]] & [[Curb Agajanian Performance Group|Curb-Agajanian]]\n|98\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Marco Andretti]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://beyondtheflag.com/2018/08/16/indycar-marco-andretti-return-andretti-herta-autosport-2019/|title=IndyCar: Marco Andretti to return to Andretti Herta Autosport in 2019|last=Fair|first=Asher|date=August 16, 2018|website=Beyond the Flag|language=en-US|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-05-28}}</ref>\n|All\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Arrow McLaren SP]]<ref name=\"McLarenSPM\">{{cite web|url=https://www.motorsport.com/indycar/news/mclaren-indycar-fulltime-arrow-spm/4510636/|title=McLaren returns to IndyCar full-time partnering 