019/12/12-10-IGP-Sponsor | title=Indianapolis Motor Speedway road race lands title sponsor}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indycar.com/News/2017/07/07-17-Toronto-notebook|title=Toronto notes: Honda Canada extends sponsorship through 2020|website=IndyCar.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=DOUBLEHEADERS AT IOWA, LAGUNA SECA, THIRD EVENT AT IMS HIGHLIGHT UPDATED INDYCAR CALENDAR|url=https://www.indycar.com/News/2020/04/04-06-Schedule-Update|date=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%\"\n|-\n!colspan=7|Cancelled events\n|-\n| April 5\n| [[Honda Indy Grand Prix of Alabama]]\n| {{Color box|lightblue|R|border=darkgray}} [[Barber Motorsports Park]]\n| colspan=2| [[Birmingham, Alabama]]\n|-\n| April 19\n| [[Grand Prix of Long Beach|Acura Grand Prix of Long Beach]]\n| {{Color box|lightblue|R|border=darkgray}} [[Grand Prix of Long Beach|Streets of Long Beach]]\n| colspan=2| [[Long Beach, California]]\n|-\n| April 26\n| [[AutoNation INDYCAR Challenge]]\n| {{Color box|lightblue|R|border=darkgray}} [[Circuit of the Americas]]\n| colspan=2| [[Austin, Texas]]\n|-\n| May 30\u201331\n| [[Detroit Grand Prix (IndyCar)|Chevrolet Detroit Grand Prix Presented by Lear Corporation]]\n| {{Color box|lightblue|R|border=darkgray}} [[Detroit Grand Prix (IndyCar)|The Raceway at Belle Isle Park]]\n| colspan=2| [[Detroit|Detroit, Michigan]]\n|-\n!colspan=7| References: <ref>{{cite web |title=Official Statement From INDYCAR |url=https://www.indycar.com/News/2020/03/03-12-StPete-Race |website=IndyCar.com |accessdate=13 March 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"GPLB cancellation\"/><ref>{{cite web|title=DOUBLEHEADERS AT IOWA, LAGUNA SECA, THIRD EVENT AT IMS HIGHLIGHT UPDATED INDYCAR CALENDAR|url=https://www.indycar.com/News/2020/04/04-06-Schedule-Update|date=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n{{legend|#FFFFFF|text=O|Short oval/Superspeedway|border=solid 1px #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|lightblue|text=R|Road/street course|border=solid 1px #AAAAAA}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[2020 Indy Lights]]\n